{
  "stem": "21089.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What-- what I could do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I just went away very upset.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, as I said, I was protected as a foreigner because I wasn't-- I wasn't a German subject, and I was-- German Jew.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wasn't an Austrian Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was comp-- foreign citizens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at that time yet, the foreign citizens yet were, were honored, even foreign Jews were honored also yet.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not the [INAUDIBLE] Later, nothing helped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, no citizenship helped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When you are a Jew, you are a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- went to many friends that I was helping.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I was-- I was buying food for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and not much I could do, but I wasn't afraid to do it because I know that I-- this not a dangers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for some people, I-- they had letters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I made letters for them-- many, many letters to foreign countries, [INAUDIBLE] writing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the-- all the mail was censorshipped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The reason I know because well, later, when I was in Vilna, and I wrote to Vienna for the copy of my graduation certificate, and it came with-- the letter was open.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this is from the Institute to me with the s-- stamp-- swastika stamps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and it was marked censorship.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody knew that many letters came--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Censored.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Censored.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Open.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whether open and-- because they been afraid that people have been sending money outside or some documents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even when I was coming home on the-- on the train, normally when you co-- go to the border, they check your documents and check you if you have-- at that time, if you have something in your [BACKGROUND NOISE] suitcases with you, which you had-- with you on your train-- on your train, were-- normally, sometimes they ask to open.",
      "word_count": 61
    }
  ],
